comment: RO SLA shows Hill (UTA) make contact with Westbrook's (OKC) face and affect his SQBR.
Oladipo (OKC) makes contact with Burks' (UTA) arms that affects his driving shot attempt.
Gobert (UTA) makes incidental contact with Adams (OKC) that does not affect his shot attempt.
Hill (UTA) makes contact with Westbrook's (OKC) body that affects his jump shot attempt.
Favors (UTA) does not make contact with Adams (OKC) on his driving shot attempt.
Favors (UTA) and Kanter (OKC) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Adams (OKC) sets the screen on the Burks (UTA) and gives him room to avoid the contact. The two players briefly engage and separate following the screen.
[Incidental or immaterial] Favors (UTA) and Kanter (OKC) engage with one another during the rebound and Favors pulls Kanter's jersey.
Adams (OKC) engages with Hill (UTA) prior to retrieving the loose ball.
Burks (UTA) commits a take foul on Westbrook (OKC).
Gobert (UTA) sets the screen on Roberson (OKC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Adams (OKC) sets the screen on Hill (UTA) and the two players continue moving up the floor. Any contact is marginal.
